 my mouth say I would do the right thing and the clean thing, and go and write to [Jim's:] owner and tell where he was; but deep down in me I knowed it was a lie--and He knowed it. You can't pray a lie -- I found that out...\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003e...It was a close place. I took it up, and held it in my hand. I was a trembling, because I'd got to decide, forever, betwixt two things, and I knowed it. I studied a minute, sort of holding my breath, and then says to myself: 'All right, then, I'll go to Hell'--and tore it up.\"","rating":5,"shelving":{"__typename":"Shelving","shelf":{"__typename":"Shelf","name":"read","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/261650?shelf=read"},"taggings":[],"webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/4226564"},"likeCount":178,"viewerHasLiked":null,"commentCount":17,"viewerCanComment({\"resourceType\":\"review\"})":null},"Book:kca://book/amzn1.gr.book.v1.kIs3h3Eglr_mGqP8cWt-XA":{"id":"kca://book/amzn1.gr.book.v1.kIs3h3Eglr_mGqP8cWt-XA","__typename":"Book"},"User:44531801":{"id":44531801,"__typename":"User","legacyId":44531801,"imageUrlSquare":"https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1533839073i/44531801._UX200_CR0,7,200,200_.jpg","isAuthor":false,"textReviewsCount":997,"viewableName":"Nayra.Hassan","isBlockedByViewer":false,"webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/user/show/44531801-nayra-hassan","contributor":null,"isFollowing":false,"isFriend":false,"followersCount":4436},"Review:kca://review:goodreads/amzn1.gr.review:goodreads.v1.h5UzDC1OY3VoNVXjxIzGqw":{"id":"kca://review:goodreads/amzn1.gr.review:goodreads.v1.h5UzDC1OY3VoNVXjxIzGqw","__typename":"Review","book":{"__ref":"Book:kca://book/amzn1.gr.book.v1.kIs3h3Eglr_mGqP8cWt-XA"},"creator":{"__ref":"User:44531801"},"recommendFor":null,"updatedAt":1640538978799,"createdAt":1500433617817,"spoilerStatus":false,"lastRevisionAt":1618991606686,"text":"\u003cb\u003eكله يدلع نفسه..بالعقل و بالاصول اوعى تدلعها زيادة\u003cbr\u003e دايما بتفكرني هذه ال